### CI integration

Add to your CI pipeline:

```yaml
# GitHub Actions example
- name: Start Pluto
  run: rebar3 shell &
       sleep 3   # wait for server to accept connections

- name: Run Pluto self-test
  run: echo '{"op":"selftest"}' | nc -q1 localhost 9000 | grep '"status":"ok"'

- name: Run scenario tests
  run: python3 tests/run_scenarios.py --host localhost --port 9000 --scenarios all
```

Exit code is non-zero on any failure so CI gates can block on test results.

